84
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:39,060
I can't drink it.

85
00:05:39,860 --> 00:05:41,260
What do you want then?

86
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:42,980
I'm not being picky.

87
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:43,900
You know

88
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:45,500
