159
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:40,060
Don't make any mistakes.

160
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:44,860
This is your duty.

161
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:18,620
I added

162
00:11:18,620 --> 00:11:19,820
