179
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:53,300
Don't be afraid. I'll protect you from now on.

180
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:54,780
Protect me?

181
00:12:57,780 --> 00:12:59,780
My power is weak,

182
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:01,820
